627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Benson_Kipruto\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Benson_Kipruto\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"silver\", \"from\": 952, \"to\": 958}, {\"ngram\": \"bronze\", \"from\": 963, \"to\": 969}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But Tola's 21sec victory was made even more impressive given the stifling conditions and a course with some venom thanks to several punishing hills.\", \"from\": 984, \"to\": 1132, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 988, \"end\": 992, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tuul_River\", \"score\": 0.9999999975370883, \"rank\": 2.3641841987441166e-09, \"text\": \"Tola\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tuul_River\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tuul_River\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the stifling conditions\", \"from\": 1045, \"to\": 1068}, {\"ngram\": \"a course\", \"from\": 1073, \"to\": 1081}, {\"ngram\": \"some venom\", \"from\": 1087, \"to\": 1097}, {\"ngram\": \"several punishing hills\", \"from\": 1108, \"to\": 1131}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The race was effectively over after 35km when Tola clocked a stunning 5km split of 14min 02sec, which is six seconds faster than the first heat of the men's 5000m round one this week.\", \"from\": 1133, \"to\": 1316, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1179, \"end\": 1183, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tuul_River\", \"score\": 0.9999999975370883, \"rank\": 2.3641841987441166e-09, \"text\": \"Tola\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tuul_River\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tuul_River\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The race\", \"from\": 1133, \"to\": 1141}, {\"ngram\": \"35km\", \"from\": 1169, \"to\": 1173}, {\"ngram\": \"a stunning 5km split\", \"from\": 1192, \"to\": 1212}, {\"ngram\": \"14min 02sec\", \"from\": 1216, \"to\": 1227}, {\"ngram\": \"the first heat\", \"from\": 1262, \"to\": 1276}, {\"ngram\": \"the men's 5000m\", \"from\": 1280, \"to\": 1295}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The course's total elevation was 1,430ft, significantly more than Boston (891ft) or New York (945ft).\", \"from\": 1318, \"to\": 1419, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1384, \"end\": 1390, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boston\", \"score\": 0.9998078057268083, \"rank\": 0.00018033056639108608, \"text\": \"Boston\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boston\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boston\"}, {\"begin\": 1402, \"end\": 1410, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\", \"score\": 0.9999999999654392, \"rank\": 3.4777812825945986e-11, \"text\": \"New York\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The course's total elevation\", \"from\": 1318, \"to\": 1346}, {\"ngram\": \"1,430ft\", \"from\": 1351, \"to\": 1358}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It did for a fading Eliud Kipchoge; the two-time defending Olympic champion could be seen walking at times before eventually stepping off the course at 31km.\", \"from\": 1420, \"to\": 1577, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1440, \"end\": 1454, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eliud_Kipchoge\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Eliud Kipchoge\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eliud_Kipchoge\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eliud_Kipchoge\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the two-time defending Olympic champion\", \"from\": 1456, \"to\": 1495}, {\"ngram\": \"times\", \"from\": 1521, \"to\": 1526}, {\"ngram\": \"the course\", \"from\": 1558, \"to\": 1568}, {\"ngram\": \"31km\", \"from\": 1572, \"to\": 1576}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But Tola made it look easy, particularly given his training block is unlikely to have been so specific, not when he was not even supposed to be in this race, having received the call just two weeks ago when compatriot Sisay Lemma pulled out injured.\", \"from\": 1579, \"to\": 1828, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1583, \"end\": 1587, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tuul_River\", \"score\": 0.9999999975370883, \"rank\": 2.3641841987441166e-09, \"text\": \"Tola\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tuul_River\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tuul_River\"}, {\"begin\": 1797, \"end\": 1808, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sisay_Lemma\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sisay Lemma\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sisay_Lemma\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sisay_Lemma\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his training block\", \"from\": 1626, \"to\": 1644}, {\"ngram\": \"this race\", \"from\": 1726, \"to\": 1735}, {\"ngram\": \"the call\", \"from\": 1753, \"to\": 1761}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After Cairess ran the race of his life, the new Olympic champion has set a daunting standard.\", \"from\": 1829, \"to\": 1922, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Cairess\", \"from\": 1835, \"to\": 1842}, {\"ngram\": \"the race\", \"from\": 1847, \"to\": 1855}, {\"ngram\": \"his life\", \"from\": 1859, \"to\": 1867}, {\"ngram\": \"the new Olympic champion\", \"from\": 1869, \"to\": 1893}, {\"ngram\": \"a daunting standard\", \"from\": 1902, \"to\": 1921}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Bradford man stormed down the blue carpet at the majestic Esplanade des Invalides soon after in 2hr 7min 29sec, with the Eiffel Tower peeking over the stands.\", \"from\": 1924, \"to\": 2086, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1928, \"end\": 1936, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bradford\", \"score\": 0.9999882740899833, \"rank\": 1.1284918117971915e-05, \"text\": \"Bradford\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bradford\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bradford\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the blue carpet\", \"from\": 1954, \"to\": 1969}, {\"ngram\": \"the majestic Esplanade des Invalides\", \"from\": 1973, \"to\": 2009}, {\"ngram\": \"2hr 7min 29sec\", \"from\": 2024, \"to\": 2038}, {\"ngram\": \"the Eiffel Tower\", \"from\": 2045, \"to\": 2061}, {\"ngram\": \"the stands\", \"from\": 2075, \"to\": 2085}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Cairess surged past Deresa Geleta of Ethiopia, a 2hr 3min man and more than three minutes faster on paper than the Briton (personal best 2hr 6min 46sec).\", \"from\": 2087, \"to\": 2240, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2124, \"end\": 2132, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ethiopia\", \"score\": 0.9999999545725596, \"rank\": 4.542714968195879e-08, \"text\": \"Ethiopia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ethiopia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ethiopia\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Cairess\", \"from\": 2087, \"to\": 2094}, {\"ngram\": \"Deresa Geleta\", \"from\": 2107, \"to\": 2120}, {\"ngram\": \"a 2hr 3min man\", \"from\": 2134, \"to\": 2148}, {\"ngram\": \"paper\", \"from\": 2187, \"to\": 2192}, {\"ngram\": \"the Briton\", \"from\": 2198, \"to\": 2208}, {\"ngram\": \"personal best 2hr 6min 46sec\", \"from\": 2210, \"to\": 2238}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But Cairess is built from the right stuff: from the Meanwood Training Camp in Leeds alongsideTeam GBteammate Phil Sesemann, who finished 46th, to the hills of Iten, Kenya and Sestriere, Italy.\", \"from\": 2241, \"to\": 2433, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2293, \"end\": 2301, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Meanwood\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Meanwood\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Meanwood\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Meanwood\"}, {\"begin\": 2319, \"end\": 2324, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leeds\", \"score\": 0.9888583972599917, \"rank\": 0.011266144772452276, \"text\": \"Leeds\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leeds\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leeds\"}, {\"begin\": 2406, \"end\": 2411, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenya\", \"score\": 0.9999999999672582, \"rank\": 3.2499272242622715e-11, \"text\": \"Kenya\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenya\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenya\"}, {\"begin\": 2427, \"end\": 2432, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy\", \"score\": 0.6886078597043698, \"rank\": 0.45220008913603676, \"text\": \"Italy\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Cairess\", \"from\": 2245, \"to\": 2252}, {\"ngram\": \"the right stuff\", \"from\": 2267, \"to\": 2282}, {\"ngram\": \"GBteammate Phil Sesemann\", \"from\": 2339, \"to\": 2363}, {\"ngram\": \"the hills\", \"from\": 2387, \"to\": 2396}, {\"ngram\": \"Iten\", \"from\": 2400, \"to\": 2404}, {\"ngram\": \"Sestriere\", \"from\": 2416, \"to\": 2425}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am pretty good at hills,\\\" Cairess said after narrowly missing out on the podium and becoming the first British Olympic medal in the men's race since Charlie Spedding in 1984.\", \"from\": 2435, \"to\": 2612, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2541, \"end\": 2548, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9999420908658608, \"rank\": 3.086170344983843e-05, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 2587, \"end\": 2603, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charlie_Spedding\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Charlie Spedding\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charlie_Spedding\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charlie_Spedding\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"hills\", \"from\": 2456, \"to\": 2461}, {\"ngram\": \"Cairess\", \"from\": 2464, \"to\": 2471}, {\"ngram\": \"the podium\", \"from\": 2507, \"to\": 2517}, {\"ngram\": \"the men's race\", \"from\": 2566, \"to\": 2580}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I tried to keep a good pace.\", \"from\": 2613, \"to\": 2642, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a good pace\", \"from\": 2630, \"to\": 2641}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The hills come naturally to me, I think that was one of the advantages for me in the race today.\", \"from\": 2643, \"to\": 2739, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The hills\", \"from\": 2643, \"to\": 2652}, {\"ngram\": \"the advantages\", \"from\": 2699, \"to\": 2713}, {\"ngram\": \"the race\", \"from\": 2724, \"to\": 2732}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I did not really care where I came, it is more about doing my best race and feeling I fulfilled my potential.\", \"from\": 2740, \"to\": 2849, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my best race\", \"from\": 2799, \"to\": 2811}, {\"ngram\": \"my potential\", \"from\": 2836, \"to\": 2848}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I can not control how fit the other guys are.\", \"from\": 2850, \"to\": 2895, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the other guys\", \"from\": 2876, \"to\": 2890}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I ran the best I could have and I am really proud of myself.\\\"\", \"from\": 2896, \"to\": 2957, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Cairess has now backed up a third place at London this year with fourth in the Olympics, a race devoid of the comforts pacers bring.\", \"from\": 2959, \"to\": 3091, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3002, \"end\": 3008, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.054778012407229e-19, \"text\": \"London\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a third place\", \"from\": 2985, \"to\": 2998}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 3034, \"to\": 3046}, {\"ngram\": \"a race\", \"from\": 3048, \"to\": 3054}, {\"ngram\": \"the comforts pacers\", \"from\": 3065, \"to\": 3084}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He's starting to prove himself as a menacing racer, rather than a machine built for a flat race resembling a time trial.\", \"from\": 3092, \"to\": 3212, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a menacing racer\", \"from\": 3126, \"to\": 3142}, {\"ngram\": \"a machine\", \"from\": 3156, \"to\": 3165}, {\"ngram\": \"a flat race\", \"from\": 3176, \"to\": 3187}, {\"ngram\": \"a time trial\", \"from\": 3199, \"to\": 3211}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Cairess has a lot to do if he is to slash several minutes off his personal best, yet the way he disposed of Geleta and other faster runners on paper suggests that will come in time.\", \"from\": 3214, \"to\": 3395, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 3226, \"to\": 3231}, {\"ngram\": \"several minutes\", \"from\": 3256, \"to\": 3271}, {\"ngram\": \"the way\", \"from\": 3299, \"to\": 3306}, {\"ngram\": \"Geleta\", \"from\": 3322, \"to\": 3328}, {\"ngram\": \"other faster runners\", \"from\": 3333, \"to\": 3353}, {\"ngram\": \"paper\", \"from\": 3357, \"to\": 3362}, {\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 3390, \"to\": 3394}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I feel like I can be up there in the majors,\\\" Cairess maintains.\", \"from\": 3397, \"to\": 3462, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the majors\", \"from\": 3431, \"to\": 3441}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's only my third marathon, I am still young.\", \"from\": 3463, \"to\": 3510, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"only my third marathon\", \"from\": 3469, \"to\": 3491}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I have big goals but I just have to take everything step by step.\", \"from\": 3511, \"to\": 3576, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"big goals\", \"from\": 3518, \"to\": 3527}, {\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 3552, \"to\": 3562}, {\"ngram\": \"step\", \"from\": 3571, \"to\": 3575}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Keep improving and working hard.\", \"from\": 3577, \"to\": 3609, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I always did cross country and I am not scared of hills.\", \"from\": 3611, \"to\": 3668, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"country\", \"from\": 3631, \"to\": 3638}, {\"ngram\": \"hills\", \"from\": 3662, \"to\": 3667}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It will be tougher to compete in [a fast, flat marathon such as] Valencia where the winning time might be 2hr 1min or 2 hr 2min, but hopefully I can get there.\", \"from\": 3669, \"to\": 3828, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3734, \"end\": 3742, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Circuit_Ricardo_Tormo\", \"score\": 0.9920290587670195, \"rank\": 0.0079962914513179, \"text\": \"Valencia\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Circuit_Ricardo_Tormo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Circuit_Ricardo_Tormo\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a fast, flat marathon\", \"from\": 3703, \"to\": 3724}, {\"ngram\": \"the winning time\", \"from\": 3749, \"to\": 3765}, {\"ngram\": \"2hr 1min\", \"from\": 3775, \"to\": 3783}, {\"ngram\": \"2 hr 2min\", \"from\": 3787, \"to\": 3796}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I just need more time, more fitness.\", \"from\": 3830, \"to\": 3867, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"more time\", \"from\": 3843, \"to\": 3852}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Running is quite simple, it's just a lot of training.\\\"\", \"from\": 3868, \"to\": 3922, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"just a lot\", \"from\": 3898, \"to\": 3908}, {\"ngram\": \"training\", \"from\": 3912, \"to\": 3920}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And in that regard, he is in good hands with the venerable Renato Canova, the veteran Italian coach who has trained a who's who of elite marathoners.\", \"from\": 3924, \"to\": 4073, \"entitie